Menu="OtherSettings"
Title="HPE Management"
Icon="server"
Tag="icon-hpe-mgmt"
---
<?PHP
/* HPE Management — unRAID settings page.
 * Config persists at /boot/config/plugins/hpe-mgmt/hpe-mgmt.cfg.
 * Save handler lives in include/settings.php.
 */

$plugin   = "hpe-mgmt";
$cfg_path = "/boot/config/plugins/$plugin/$plugin.cfg";
$defaults = parse_ini_file("/usr/local/emhttp/plugins/$plugin/plugin/$plugin.cfg.default");
$current  = file_exists($cfg_path) ? parse_ini_file($cfg_path) : $defaults;

$stack    = $current['STACK']     ?? 'modern';
$extras   = $current['EXTRAS']    ?? '';
$mcp_dist = $current['MCP_DIST']  ?? 'CentOS';
$mcp_ver  = $current['MCP_VER']   ?? '8';
$gpg      = $current['VERIFY_GPG'] ?? '1';

$extras_set = array_flip(preg_split('/\s+/', trim($extras)));
function is_extra($extras_set, $k) { return isset($extras_set[$k]) ? "checked" : ""; }
function sel_stack($stack, $v)     { return $stack === $v ? "checked" : ""; }

/* Service status (best effort). */
$rc = "/etc/rc.d/rc.hpe-mgmt";
$status = is_executable($rc) ? shell_exec("$rc status 2>&1") : "(not yet installed)";
?>

<form markdown="1" name="hpe_mgmt_form" method="POST"
      action="/plugins/hpe-mgmt/include/settings.php" target="progressFrame">

Stack to install and run:
: <input type="radio" name="STACK" value="modern" <?=sel_stack($stack,'modern')?>> Modern (amsd + ssacli + hponcfg)  —  recommended
  <input type="radio" name="STACK" value="legacy" <?=sel_stack($stack,'legacy')?>> Legacy SMH (hpsmh + CMA + :2381)
  <input type="radio" name="STACK" value="both"   <?=sel_stack($stack,'both')?>>   Both

Extra packages:
: <input type="checkbox" name="EX_ssaducli" <?=is_extra($extras_set,'ssaducli')?>> ssaducli (Smart Storage diagnostics)
  <input type="checkbox" name="EX_storcli"  <?=is_extra($extras_set,'storcli')?>>  storcli (LSI/Broadcom RAID)
  <input type="checkbox" name="EX_hponcfg"  <?=is_extra($extras_set,'hponcfg')?>>  hponcfg (iLO config from OS)
  <input type="checkbox" name="EX_diag"     <?=is_extra($extras_set,'diag')?>>     HPE Offline Diagnostics

HPE SDR distribution:
: <select name="MCP_DIST">
    <?php foreach (['CentOS','Alma','OracleLinux'] as $d):
        $s = $d === $mcp_dist ? 'selected' : ''; ?>
      <option <?=$s?>><?=$d?></option>
    <?php endforeach; ?>
  </select>
  version
  <select name="MCP_VER">
    <?php foreach (['7','8','9','current'] as $v):
        $s = $v === $mcp_ver ? 'selected' : ''; ?>
      <option <?=$s?>><?=$v?></option>
    <?php endforeach; ?>
  </select>

Verify GPG signatures:
: <input type="checkbox" name="VERIFY_GPG" value="1" <?=($gpg=='1'?'checked':'')?>> (strongly recommended)

&nbsp;
: <input type="submit" name="apply"  value="Apply (install/reinstall)">
  <input type="submit" name="restart" value="Restart services">

Service status:
: <pre style="font-family:monospace; white-space:pre-wrap;"><?=htmlspecialchars($status)?></pre>
</form>
